Detailed Description

cvmx_mio_uart::_sbcr

The shadow break control register is a shadow register for the MIO_UART(0..1)_LCR[BRK] bit that can be used to remove the burden of having to perform a read- modify-write on MIO_UART(0..1)_LCR.
